CAKE
Step 1: Mix milk,eggs,flour and butter in a bowl
Step 2: Mix until smooth
Step 3: Pour in batter of your choice and heat oven up to 120 degrees celcius
Step 4: After oven has been heated up for 15 minutes,place batter in the oven and wait for 40-45 minutes

FROSTING
Step 1: While cake is baking, mix all the frosting ingredients(milk,creame,condesed milk,butter,egg,vanilla essence/strawerry milk/cocoa)
Step 2: Mix until smooth, then place it in the fridge for 15 minutes to cool(DO NOT PLACE IT IN THE FREEZER!)

Once the cake and frosting are ready, place the cake outsite to cool for 30 minutes
Then, spread the frosting and enjoy